          "source_snapshot_id": "snap-91520bafa7ae1dfc",
          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-d947fdd72018b30f",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "the Preferred Package\nThere\u2019s\u00a0no minimum balance\u00a0required\u00a0to open a Scotiabank Preferred Package.\nYou\u2019re responsible for having enough money in your account to cover any fees, such as your monthly account fee. If your balance is $0 or less, you may be charged additional fees, such as a non-sufficient funds (NSF) fee. Accounts with a balance of $0 or less that remain inactive may be closed.\nEven though you\u00a0don\u2019t\u00a0need to\u00a0maintain\u00a0a minimum balance, you can waive the monthly account fee by holding\u00a0a\u00a0 minimum\u00a0balance.\nYou\u2019ll pay no monthly account fee by holding $4,000 or more in your Preferred Package every day for the entire month.\nThe Preferred Package offers our most popular features packaged for our customers\u2019 everyday banking needs.\nPreferred Package account holders can take advantage of various fee waivers and preferred rates across other product categories. Check out our full list",
