          "field_name": "eligibility_text",
          "candidate_value": "The Scotiabank Cash Bonus Bundle Offer (the \u201cOffer\u201d) is available between March 3, 2026, and July 2, 2026 (the \u201cOffer Period\u201d), to individuals who open new eligible accounts",
