          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-1d2ad61decbfddae",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "banking package\nHighlights\nMore benefits\nUnlimited debit transactions 3\nFirst year annual fee\u00a0rebate\u00a0up to $150 on select credit cards 4\nNo monthly account fee on a Scotia\u00ae U.S. Dollar Daily Interest Account 5\n20 free Scotia\u00a0iTRADE stock or ETF trades in your 1st\u00a0year 6\nScene+ TM points 13\n$1.99 Scotia International Money Transfers 7\nUnlimited Interac\u00a0e-Transfer \u2020 transactions\nEligible for overdraft protection 8\nExtra 0.05% interest on your Momentum PLUS Savings Account 9\n1 free ABM withdrawal in Canada a month 10\nPreferred rates on select GICs 11",
